latestPosts.caption: Khushi ke aansu.. well done RCB !! Such a proud fan !!! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️ played like true champions boys !!! What a lovely final !!! Well tried Punjab !! Had my heart in my mouth !! Uffff cricket you beauty !!!

KD was the antagonist . But he was also hurting. Also hiding. Also human.
To play him was to break rules and hearts - mine included.
Thank you for seeing the grey in his black.
And thank you for this award…
Never thought being the bad guy would feel this damn good. 😈🖤
(Mom still says I was her hero. So that’s sorted.)

Thank you to the creators - @rajanddk and @mensit for letting me fly with this 🙏❤️

Thank you @castingchhabra and his team for bringing  this to me ❤️

Thank you @primevideoin for my first with you guys ❤️

And thank you to all my lovely co actors - Varun , Samantha , Kay Kay sir , Sikku , Kashvi (you cutie) , Armaan and everyone else I shared screen with on this one ❤️

And last but not the least @talentrackofficial for the recognition .
